      "settings": {
        "text_fDKyQrimwHJll2Fb": "<p>THE CARBINOX EDGE IS BACK IN STOCK — ONLY 1,000 PCS!</p>",
        "text_nWc21VEEBLfHqJ5V": "<p><strong>THE FIRST STAINLESS-STEEL MODEL EVER MADE AT CARBINOX IS NOW AVAILABLE!</strong></p>",
        "product_dVypRhlscBgS0zLr": "",
        "text_o6wmJsptXak3lbi7": "<p>GET CARBINOX EDGE NOW➔</p>",
        "text_vQaIGV68wADt7PKv": "<p>WE&apos;RE EXPERIENCING HIGH DEMAND RIGHT NOW!</p>",
        "text_X0js3H3P7n2LB2k3": "<p>DURABILITY AND </p><p>RELIABILITY, BEYOND REALITY.</p>",
        "text_uqvMytjcYL3bkwN8": "<p>DURABILITY </p><p>AND RELIABILITY, BEYOND REALITY.</p>",
        "text_fiNH0Ha6sCEIk4Gc": "<p>Rugged Smartwatches and Gear that works as hard as you do.</p>",
        "text_xvC7Zbh8vCMMVMyD": "<p>Tough as nails durability for the field.</p>",
        "text_WYQYR2Pyn28HuVWR": "<p>Lifetime warranty for all our products.</p>",
        "text_04UqIsbZr0aZwTxX": "<p>Gear that lasts more without breaking the bank.</p>",
        "product_Ic4xCj1VBs34XCBQ": "",
        "text_PrDFrbwHcC2OSU7P": "<p>shop now ➔</p>",
        "text_IX1MWJ8SfBOejfKI": "<p>Trusted by 350,000+ hard workers nationwide.</p>",
        "text_GVa4O8YXXY7cCF65": "<p>3 Reasons to Choose </p>",
        "text_kZ45robCifuIgH3A": "<p>Carbinox Gear Today:</p>",
        "text_Siayk0I2yzWzvO3S": "<p>Built for the bold</p>",
        "text_BmZv4knf2FMBNnob": "<p>Tough as nails shockproof, waterproof,</p><p>and built to handle the grind.</p>",
        "text_5ysQuuPXS9Q0uoNK": "<p>Stay connected and ready</p>",
        "text_XlpmjMGaL8GfBVhm": "<p>From smartwatches to accessories, stay connected, organized, and prepared for anything on your wrist and beyond.</p>",
        "text_wxG78oDmvruyJbQM": "<p>Unmatched durability</p>",
        "text_EVwDrnOmo9nvuMdl": "<p>Rugged, reliable, and built to endure. Carbinox products are crafted to last and support you through the toughest environments.</p>",
        "url_TSbEtH51uQER6gh3": "",
        "text_6R7u5maTswUNS8Mv": "<p>shop now ➔</p>",
        "text_riiQHbM0tNlbgMSh": "<p>Trusted by 350,000+ hard workers nationwide.</p>",
        "text_Lt25ebgVhpCbzjr4": "<p>“If I wanted all the toughness and functions available in this smartwatch, I’d have to wear five from other brands at the same time”</p>",
        "text_drlCPxzqwfMIPzWc": "<p>Robert K. - Operator</p>",
        "text_eJpmHqD8IGsL1ANd": "<p>\"The Blaze is hands-down my favorite. I'm glad I skipped the overpriced name brands. This thing gives you 10X the value for a fraction of the cost. Built tough, works like a charm, and doesn't break the bank.\"</p>",
        "text_D4EqsyFIeana07GM": "<p>Tony M. - Manager</p>",
        "text_XmcLJZvRWZDm8QxT": "<p>\"This is the only watch that's actually kept up with me. I've dropped it, slammed it, scratched the hell out of it and it just keeps going. It's like it laughs in the face of abuse. Told all my guys to grab one too.\"</p>",
        "text_PBR74t4tJ7urGBQ8": "<p>Zachary B.  - Owner & Mechanic</p>",
        "text_q2ytt3S8omlshyIo": "<p>\"The amount of bands and gear I got with my watch was insane. I thought the price was too good to be real-but when it showed up, man, I was pumped. Solid build, great value, no BS.\"</p>",
        "text_wV7ITI4BWliAIBKh": "<p>Vannary Y.  - Construction Worker</p>",
        "text_yZn0lHFa80ukDkaf": "<p>Tough gear for everyday grind.</p>",
        "text_fqPgYpG1Cn9BNeDB": "<p>Check our collection:</p>",
        "url_RbbiOQNU1DfNwuTP": "",
        "url_HqviSGcthw8Agl80": "",
        "url_Fyn6hYlbQ68D452p": "",
        "url_FpSoQ5bTCgHR6FX4": "",
        "text_Stb5Ge1TeBUKwPLp": "<p>Get ready to stay connected,</p><p>even on the roughest conditions.</p>",
        "text_68JgVQHVxNJrydkj": "<p>THE CARBINOX SOLUTION</p>",
        "text_qF4GbauaTinS65js": "<p>Tough Watches</p>",
        "text_wEmBlYlWHuAouTNt": "<p>for Real Men</p>",
        "text_hfheS2zfRFq21mLy": "<p>Extreme</p><p>Durability</p>",
        "text_aeKK1qL5danOpoOd": "<p>Impact &</p><p>Scratch Resistant</p>",
        "text_9DZU4ALnEsYA6sUZ": "<p>Lifetime</p><p>Warranty</p>",
        "product_XiCUJBHezgca4rlI": "",
        "text_PaY9ib0hoXfN3KH8": "<p>shop now ➔</p>",
        "text_7LoL3D8lU8taCGHM": "<p>Trusted by 350,000+ hard workers nationwide.</p>",
        "text_flUnNzOdOGzci7kr": "<p>Would your current watch resist this?</p>",
        "text_3HQ9ZtXP9l7ntAFc": "<p>BIG TRUCK TEST</p>",
        "text_H60VMMoaLOFpCeUK": "<p>The Blaze survived under a truck, thanks to its zinc alloy body and Gorilla Glass—no scratches, no problem.</p>",
        "text_r7SODBN7EDGlhdmH": "<p>WATER TEST</p>",
        "text_rQI7jxBBCQauiEk4": "<p>With IP69K water resistance, the Blaze handles water like a pro—swim, shower, or rain, it keeps going strong.</p>",
        "text_XGJxJlDGeDNJNkpp": "<p>DROP TEST</p>",
        "text_ams5aoVJQbgZk3PG": "<p>No worries, this watch took a tumble and brushed it off. The shockproof design keeps the screen clear and sensors accurate.</p>",
        "text_zd8uXauI4qaYebLI": "<p>DUMBBELL TEST</p>",
        "text_ULeuOdkj16OuI7x8": "<p>Serious impact? No problem. The reinforced body and durable materials make the Carbinox Blaze practically indestructible.</p>",
        "text_WD3I2V6XPgXV2nnT": "<p>STRAP FLEXIBILITY TEST</p>",
        "text_ifeU9ggo83j3mimm": "<p>The Carbinox Blaze straps are ultra-flexible and tough — built to move with you without sacrificing comfort.</p>",
        "text_RNyrUWT99oYeroHv": "<p>FRYING EGGS TEST </p>",
        "text_sXskEPXMTACKLC1G": "<p>Heat and egg-resistant, the Blaze can handle wild challenges. Maybe don’t cook with it daily… but it’ll survive if you do!</p>",
        "text_nP2twbiegoBSyIVV": "<p>CREATING EVERYDAY</p>",
        "text_KKkEFEWJJc8YtIlm": "<p>OUTDOOR ARTILLERY</p>",
        "text_x1XLSuYBZuqxeprl": "<p><strong>Our mission is to deliver gear that earns its keep and keeps you powered through it all.</strong></p>",
        "url_FotgaHES91Usxwe1": "",
        "url_fs7hrU0152kwx0Sg": "",
