        "text_VEYlYefNkNe0IuFh": "<p><strong>BREAK IT. WE&apos;LL REPLACE IT.</strong></p>",
        "text_Bb5LT5MDuKifm6Hu": "<p>If your watch ever fails, we&apos;ll send you a new one FOR FREE. No questions asked.</p>",
