        "text_FGThbAFhiVzsXL3i": "<p>\"The Blaze is hands-down my favorite. I'm glad I skipped the overpriced name brands. This thing gives you 10X the value for a fraction of the cost. Built tough, works like a charm, and doesn't break the bank.\"</p>",
