        "text_nvZobcIycY205Mns": "<p>\"This is the only watch that's actually kept up with me. I've dropped it, slammed it, scratched the hell out of it and it just keeps going. It's like it laughs in the face of abuse. Told all my guys to grab one too.\"</p>",
